{
  "page": "Walda Rivers (daughter of Aemon)",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For others with the same name, see <a href=\"/index.php/Walda_Rivers_(disambiguation)\" title=\"Walda Rivers (disambiguation)\">Walda Rivers (disambiguation)</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\">Walda Rivers</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Aemon_Rivers_and_Walda_Rivers_by_coldraindropsss.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Aemon Rivers and Walda Rivers by coldraindropsss.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/ca/Aemon_Rivers_and_Walda_Rivers_by_coldraindropsss.jpg/300px-Aemon_Rivers_and_Walda_Rivers_by_coldraindropsss.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"296\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/ca/Aemon_Rivers_and_Walda_Rivers_by_coldraindropsss.jpg/450px-Aemon_Rivers_and_Walda_Rivers_by_coldraindropsss.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/ca/Aemon_Rivers_and_Walda_Rivers_by_coldraindropsss.jpg/600px-Aemon_Rivers_and_Walda_Rivers_by_coldraindropsss.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>Walda Rivers and her father Aemon Rivers by coldraindropsss</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Frey\" title=\"House Frey\">House Frey</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Rivermen\" title=\"Rivermen\">Rivermen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_294_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">294&#160;AC</a> or <a href=\"/index.php/295_AC\" title=\"295 AC\">295&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Father</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Aemon_Rivers\" title=\"Aemon Rivers\">Aemon Rivers</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> (appears)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Walda Rivers</b> is the daughter of Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Aemon_Rivers\" title=\"Aemon Rivers\">Aemon Rivers</a>. She is a great-granddaughter of <a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Frey\" title=\"Walder Frey\">Walder Frey</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_the_Crossing\" title=\"Lord of the Crossing\">Lord of the Crossing</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Storm_of_Swords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Family\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Family</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Character\">Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Walda_Rivers_(daughter_of_Aemon)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Walda is no more than four.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Walda_Rivers_(daughter_of_Aemon)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Walda_Rivers_(daughter_of_Aemon)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>When <a href=\"/index.php/Robb_Stark\" title=\"Robb Stark\">Robb Stark</a> comes to the <a href=\"/index.php/Twins\" title=\"Twins\">Twins</a> for <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Wedding\" title=\"Red Wedding\">the wedding</a> of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Edmure_Tully\" title=\"Edmure Tully\">Edmure Tully</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Roslin_Frey\" title=\"Roslin Frey\">Roslin Frey</a>, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Frey\" title=\"Walder Frey\">Walder Frey</a> has Robb apologize to the women of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Frey\" title=\"House Frey\">House Frey</a> for having married <a href=\"/index.php/Jeyne_Westerling\" title=\"Jeyne Westerling\">Jeyne Westerling</a> instead of a Frey. Walda sneaks in among the trueborn children and curtsies when Walder asks her name.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Walda_Rivers_(daughter_of_Aemon)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Walder</b>: Heh, are you another Walda?<br />\n</p><p><b>Walda</b>: I'm Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Aemon_Rivers\" title=\"Aemon Rivers\">Aemon Rivers</a>'s Walda, lord great grandfather.<br />\n</p>\n<b>Walder</b>: How long have you been talking? Not that you're like to have anything sensible to say, your father never did. He's <a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Rivers\" title=\"Walder Rivers\">a bastard's</a> son besides, heh. Go away, I wanted only <a href=\"/index.php/House_Frey\" title=\"House Frey\">Freys</a> up here. The <a href=\"/index.php/King_in_the_North\" title=\"King in the North\">King in the North</a> has no interest in base stock.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Frey\" title=\"Walder Frey\">Walder Frey</a> and Walda</cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Walda_Rivers_(daughter_of_Aemon)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover